Chinese Hamster Ovary cell MFA model.
The core of the model is originally from:
Altamirano C, Illanes A, Casablancas A, Gámez X, Cairó JJ, Gòdia C. Analysis of CHO cells metabolic redistribution in a glutamate-based defined medium in continuous culture. Biotechnol Prog. 2001 Nov-Dec;17(6):1032-41. PubMed PMID:11735437.
Model modified slightly and converted to SBML format for BMC manuscript:
Sokolenko S, Quattrociocchi M, Aucoin MGA. Identifying model error in metabolic flux analysis -- A generalized least squares approach. BMC Systems Biology.
